WEBVTT

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.056
You drink.

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.696
And I did --

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:04.920
a lot.

00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:07.120
My story is not unique.

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:11.640
Like millions of Americans,
my disease progressed undiagnosed.

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.376
It took me to people
and places and things

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.880
that I never would have chosen.

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:20.016
It wasn't until
an intersection with the law

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:23.240
gave me an "opportunity" to get care,

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:25.800
that I began my journey of recovery.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:31.000
My journey of recovery
has been filled with love and with joy,